Users:
    Id (PK)
    Email (UNIQUE)
    First Name
    Last Name
    Password
    Salt
    Temp

Friends:
    ID
    USER_ONE
    USER_TWO
    STATUS (1=FRIENDS | 2=PENDING | 3=REJECTED)
    Date Created|Modified|Deleted

Rooms:
    ID (PK)
    Owner (Soft FK)
    Name
    Key (passphrase)
    Private (boolean)
    Location (lat/long?)
    Date Created|Modified|Deleted

Games:
    ID (PK)
    ROOM (FK)
    Winner (Soft FK)
    Date Created|Modified|Deleted
    Balls: 


